  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK915">
<l>potunalattār puṉṉalam tōyār matinalattiṉ </l>
<l>māṇṭa vaṟivi ṉavar.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those whose knowledge is made excellent by their (natural) sense will not covet the trffling delights of those whose favours are common (to all).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
